        %p.message__upper-info__toker メンバー
        %p.message__upper-info__date　2019/12/01(wed) 00:00:10
      .message__text 今日の天気は曇りのち雨です。
    .form
      .form__input-box
        .form__input-box__text
          %textarea{ placeholder: 'type a message' }
        %label{class: "form__input-box__image"}
          = icon('far', 'image')
          %input{type: "file"}
      .form__submit
      = link_to '', class: 'form__submit-btn' do
        send